For the last 2 weeks or so, I have been playing a lot of League of Legends. What frequently happens is that it will try summoning after champion select, but the screen will just go black and the cursor will be normal, and not the league cursor. I try reconnecting several times and it says - you have lost connection to the server, please try reconnecting many times, even though my internet is working fine. This really frustrates me because i have been placed into lower priority queue twice now, and can&#039;t do anything about it since it is not my fault.

There are no programs that might be harming anything, since I recently restored my computer to factory defaults.

Please help, it is getting _really annoying._{{item:3070}}
